data.description: Don’t miss out on this charming two-story home in the sought after Croixwood neighborhood. Pride of ownership shines throughout this meticulously maintained and tastefully decorated 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home that features a versatile main level with inviting tiled foyer, spacious sun-filled living room, updated custom kitchen with granite counters, separate formal dining room, dinette w/bay window, cozy family room w/gas fireplace, and convenient deck that overlooks the private fenced backyard. Upstairs enjoy 4 bedrooms on one level, including the private primary suite with updated bath and walk-in tiled shower. The finished lookout lower level offers an expansive family room that is great for entertaining, additional bedroom, bathroom, laundry, and large area for storage. Many of the completed updates throughout include flooring, baths, mechanicals, windows, siding, and roof. Located just steps away to Northland Park with pickleball courts, playground, ball fields, and hockey rink.
